# Interactive Prototype

## Description

The Smart Online Shopping application includes a fully interactive prototype created in Figma. Users can navigate through the application as they would in a real shopping experience.

### Prototype Features

- Login and Registration
- Home Page Navigation
- Product Browsing
- Product Details
- Adding Cart
- Shopping Cart
- Checkout Process
- Order Confirmation
- User Profile Navigation

